What if something dangerous happens?

00:03:17.252 --> 00:03:17.893
Lady Lan.

00:03:18.590 --> 00:03:19.573
What are you doing here?

00:03:32.692 --> 00:03:33.812
Mo.

00:03:35.932 --> 00:03:36.853
Mo.

00:03:37.293 --> 00:03:39.092
You've lost weight, Mo.

00:03:40.412 --> 00:03:41.750
- You've lost weight.
- Lady Lan.

00:03:45.013 --> 00:03:45.773
Mo.

00:03:48.573 --> 00:03:49.293
Lady Lan.

00:03:49.493 --> 00:03:50.412
It's not Mo.

00:03:50.420 --> 00:03:52.493
It's the little stray cat in the bureau,
called Mei.

00:03:53.013 --> 00:03:54.013
It is Mo.

00:03:55.652 --> 00:03:57.173
When I was sleeping today,

00:03:57.493 --> 00:03:58.893
it climbed into my bed.

00:04:00.212 --> 00:04:01.013
It's Mo.

00:04:01.293 --> 00:04:02.532
Mo came to find me.

00:04:02.692 --> 00:04:03.692
Right, Mo?

00:04:05.812 --> 00:04:07.252
So you chased it all the way here?

00:04:13.932 --> 00:04:14.893
- Mo.
- Lady Lan.

00:04:15.092 --> 00:04:16.252
It really isn't Mo.

00:04:16.533 --> 00:04:18.372
If it was, how could it scratched you?

00:04:21.853 --> 00:04:22.812
It is Mo.

00:04:23.012 --> 00:04:23.772
It is.

00:04:26.173 --> 00:04:28.372
Mo, no matter what you become,

00:04:28.493 --> 00:04:29.812
I will always love you, okay?

00:04:33.653 --> 00:04:36.853
Look, the moon is so full tonight.

00:04:37.572 --> 00:04:40.293
Let's watch the first ray
of sunlight together.

00:04:41.900 --> 00:04:43.213
I understand the pain of longing.

00:04:44.173 --> 00:04:44.853
Lady Lan.

00:04:45.630 --> 00:04:46.812
Why don't you come down first?

00:04:47.293 --> 00:04:48.493
Tomorrow I will talk to you.

00:04:51.692 --> 00:04:52.653
What do you mean?

00:04:52.660 --> 00:04:54.332
What does it mean
that you pushed me away?

00:04:54.493 --> 00:04:55.413
Mo.

00:04:56.012 --> 00:04:57.572
- Mo, I missed you so much.
- Lady Lan.

00:04:57.812 --> 00:04:58.692
Mo.

00:05:03.162 --> 00:05:06.187
(Holding Pearls and Jade)

00:05:11.973 --> 00:05:13.452
Do you feel any discomfort?

00:05:14.572 --> 00:05:15.053
Not at all.

00:05:15.892 --> 00:05:16.772
Silly girl.

00:05:17.372 --> 00:05:18.892
You don't even know that you are sick.

00:05:19.772 --> 00:05:21.413
What do you mean by this, Ms. Tong?

00:05:21.653 --> 00:05:23.413
I have always been healthy.

00:05:30.293 --> 00:05:31.812
I guess your sense of pain is gone.

00:05:32.812 --> 00:05:33.533
Last night

00:05:34.413 --> 00:05:36.293
was a sign that your mind
was collapsing.

00:05:38.733 --> 00:05:41.332
I just tolerate pain better
than most people.

00:05:41.653 --> 00:05:42.533
Is that a disease?

00:05:43.452 --> 00:05:44.390
The root of your illness

00:05:44.812 --> 00:05:46.093
is not in the body,

00:05:46.613 --> 00:05:48.173
but in the mind.

00:05:49.252 --> 00:05:50.692
You desire something you cannot have

00:05:50.700 --> 00:05:51.790
and it turns into obsession.

00:05:52.533 --> 00:05:53.733
Obsession is like poison.

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:54.973
If unresolved for a day,

00:05:55.332 --> 00:05:56.892
it erodes your senses day and night,

00:05:57.812 --> 00:05:59.692
turning you into someone
who feels no pain,

00:06:00.413 --> 00:06:02.173
a monster without emotions or desires.

00:06:06.213 --> 00:06:06.932
Monster?

00:06:07.470 --> 00:06:09.450
Is there anything wrong
with following your path?

00:06:10.892 --> 00:06:12.053
Is it wrong?

00:06:17.653 --> 00:06:19.493
Following your path is not wrong.

00:06:20.372 --> 00:06:20.932
However,

00:06:21.692 --> 00:06:23.293
what waxes must wane.

00:06:26.853 --> 00:06:28.012
If you indulge in obsession,

00:06:28.290 --> 00:06:29.413
and feed your inner demons,

00:06:30.613 --> 00:06:32.252
you will gradually lose sight

00:06:32.653 --> 00:06:34.772
of whether what you see is a demon,

00:06:35.093 --> 00:06:36.332
or your own reflection.

00:06:38.533 --> 00:06:40.572
If this continues, one day,

00:06:41.932 --> 00:06:42.772
you will become

00:06:42.892 --> 00:06:44.493
a monster nurtured by your inner demons.

00:06:45.293 --> 00:06:45.892
And then...

00:06:46.973 --> 00:06:47.452
You

00:06:48.533 --> 00:06:49.533
will still be you?

00:07:08.932 --> 00:07:10.093
Rest here for a while.

00:07:25.012 --> 00:07:26.093
(These years,)

00:07:26.812 --> 00:07:28.252
(I've been planning every day,)

00:07:28.812 --> 00:07:30.213
(and driven by obsession.)

00:07:31.093 --> 00:07:32.252
(Is it really wrong?)

00:07:33.372 --> 00:07:34.692
(This time I must first find)

00:07:34.710 --> 00:07:36.173
(the man with the tattoo on his face)

00:07:36.932 --> 00:07:38.932
(before talking about letting go
of obsession.)

00:07:43.413 --> 00:07:44.892
Miss Lan, my name is Yin.

00:07:45.053 --> 00:07:46.173
(Jade Spy Bureau officer, Yin)
Ms. Tong asked me to take care of you.

00:07:47.493 --> 00:07:48.452
To let go,

00:07:49.372 --> 00:07:50.973
but now is not the time.

00:07:52.962 --> 00:07:54.400
(Chinese New Year's Eve, tattoo under eyes)

00:08:00.293 --> 00:08:00.932
Yin.

00:08:01.533 --> 00:08:02.932
Do you know that in our bureau

00:08:03.173 --> 00:08:04.692
there is a servant named Yang Wei?

00:08:05.173 --> 00:08:06.932
Indeed, there is a servant
named Yang Wei.

00:08:08.213 --> 00:08:09.332
Could you take me to see him?

00:08:09.932 --> 00:08:10.452
Alright.

00:08:16.332 --> 00:08:17.613
Look. Is this the one?

00:08:23.737 --> 00:08:24.687
(Jade Spy Bureau coachman, Yang Wei)

00:08:25.293 --> 00:08:26.012
Who are you?

00:08:29.252 --> 00:08:30.093
(Not him.)

00:08:31.213 --> 00:08:32.450
Have you ever been to Ning City

00:08:32.772 --> 00:08:34.093
and met a man named Chen Huanfeng?

00:08:34.213 --> 00:08:36.172
(Jade Spy Bureau coachman, Yang Wei)
I have been to Ning City.

00:08:36.973 --> 00:08:39.052
Who do you mean?

00:08:42.093 --> 00:08:43.093
About this tall,

00:08:43.372 --> 00:08:44.213
left-handed.

00:08:46.252 --> 00:08:47.012
That strange man.

00:08:50.412 --> 00:08:51.973
He gave me 50 taels of silver

00:08:52.213 --> 00:08:53.372
and asked me to chat with him.

00:08:53.853 --> 00:08:54.973
He said chat,

00:08:55.292 --> 00:08:56.532
but he never spoke to me.

00:08:56.813 --> 00:08:57.973
Always staring out the window,

00:08:58.532 --> 00:08:59.772
sat like that for two hours.

00:08:59.973 --> 00:09:00.652
Then he left.

00:09:04.693 --> 00:09:05.813
(Could it be Chen Huanfeng)

00:09:06.453 --> 00:09:08.093
(has long noticed the spies around him,)

00:09:08.813 --> 00:09:09.973
(and deliberately set us up?)

00:09:15.813 --> 00:09:17.052
(Now the clues are gone.)

00:09:17.733 --> 00:09:18.853
(Could it be fate?)

00:09:19.933 --> 00:09:21.573
(I am ultimately trapped by obsession.)

00:09:22.213 --> 00:09:23.390
(Have I taken the wrong path?)

00:09:23.892 --> 00:09:25.412
Miss Lan, are you alright?

00:09:26.693 --> 00:09:27.372
Miss Lan.

00:09:27.652 --> 00:09:29.052
I don't know what happened to you.

00:09:29.333 --> 00:09:31.213
But everything will be fine.

00:09:49.100 --> 00:09:50.652
The Jade Spy Bureau people bullied you?

00:09:51.132 --> 00:09:51.933
No.

00:09:52.093 --> 00:09:53.750
It was the Jade Spy Bureau who saved me.

00:09:54.132 --> 00:09:55.733
I used to beg on the streets

00:09:56.132 --> 00:09:57.220
and blocked a noble's path,

00:09:57.230 --> 00:09:59.090
almost beaten to death
by the noble's servants.

00:09:59.412 --> 00:10:00.573
Jade Spy Bureau saved me,

00:10:00.813 --> 00:10:01.652
treated my wounds

00:10:01.813 --> 00:10:02.853
and gave me enough food.

00:10:06.733 --> 00:10:07.772
Have you ever thought

00:10:08.412 --> 00:10:09.813
to make those nobles pay?

00:10:11.093 --> 00:10:11.892
At first,

00:10:12.333 --> 00:10:13.772
I had nightmares every night.

00:10:14.050 --> 00:10:15.613
In the dream, I was starving to death

00:10:15.693 --> 00:10:16.693
or beaten to death.

00:10:18.213 --> 00:10:19.453
Ms. Tong told me

00:10:19.733 --> 00:10:21.772
that these are nightmare beasts
born of obsession.

00:10:25.372 --> 00:10:26.132
Thanks to Ms. Tong,

00:10:26.140 --> 00:10:27.652
she made this protective doll for me.

00:10:27.933 --> 00:10:28.772
As long as I wear it,

00:10:28.933 --> 00:10:30.252
I can sleep through the night.

00:10:34.493 --> 00:10:37.292
Soon Ms. Tong will send me
to the embroidery workshop to learn skills.

00:10:37.532 --> 00:10:38.333
When I learn,

00:10:38.573 --> 00:10:40.333
I will make a protective doll
for you too.

00:11:12.333 --> 00:11:13.372
Lan Mengyan.

00:11:16.453 --> 00:11:18.012
I will never allow anyone

00:11:18.070 --> 00:11:19.693
to ruin the good name of the Liu family!

00:11:20.772 --> 00:11:21.292
Qing!

00:11:22.693 --> 00:11:23.372
Qing!

00:11:25.613 --> 00:11:26.252
Qing!

00:11:30.772 --> 00:11:32.853
Qing, why are you only here now?

00:11:33.252 --> 00:11:34.772
I thought you abandoned me too.

00:12:03.493 --> 00:12:04.573
(Obsession has deepened.)

00:12:05.892 --> 00:12:07.372
(Lost sense of pain.)